    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Los Angeles California August 12th 1952",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Last Sunday my wife and I attended a Moving picture where they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "showed the Flying Saucer it looked like a spot of light",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "It gave me the impression that there might be a plane up in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "sky with a spot light or search light that is send down from the plane",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "and when our plan is make an effort to go up there to find them",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "they turn off the light and there for we feel that they have made a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "fast getaway up into the sky at a very fast speed this plane goes back",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "to its air field or to another place and fool the public",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "If our plane on its way up to find this plane would go up with all the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "lights turned off and stay far away and try to come over the top",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "of this plane they would be able to catch it but they should be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "prepared to shoot it out if needed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "I think in order to prove this idea we should send one of our own",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "plane up and have them send down a spot light or search light to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "find out if this is not true",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "If this is of any help it will make us happy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "I dont think I am very off",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Sincerely",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "[REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
